  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective of this study is to assess the ability of Fiber-optic Evanescent Wave
      Spectroscopy (FEWS) to discriminate synovial fluids samples of septic arthritis patients from
      other causes of joint effusion by analyzing ex vivo joint fluid samples collected during
      routine clinical care.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
